reviewText: This is a fully loaded bag of life truths I recommend anyone to have.

I agree with the first review about the home course being true to the live workshop and getting the same breakthroughs as the actual event.

I absolutely love this course and choose a different pillar to focus on each time I do this home event (Financial, Relational, Mental/Emotional, Physical and Spiritual) with astonishing results. Each time becomes more subtle and deeper in reaching aspects of my unconscious mind and working on my new paradigms. It is well worth the money if you are willing to go 3-for-3: Thoughts, Feelings and Actions playing full-on. It will definately affect your 'Total Belief System' in ways you could not imagine for major block breakthroughs.
